data.description: This home is a combination of old and new. Original trim and doors with updated Kitchen and bathrooms set this home apart. New appliances in the kitchen with all the white cabinets and natural light makes this kitchen a joy to cook in. Fully fenced in yard with lush landscaping, a paver and concrete patio and covered porch makes this an enjoyable back yard to enjoy year round. home has 3 bedrooms up and a first floor bedroom that could be used as a den. The storage in this home of this age, from the built-ins in the dining room and fourth bedroom to the walk in closet in the master bedroom is truly amazing. The master bath includes a claw foot tub and and a a 4 x 7 foot walk in shower. This Northeast Elgin location is close to everything to downtown Elgin for entertainment to I 90 to travel wherever you desire. This home will not last.
